  "description": "A captivating long-distance shot depicts a serene coastal landscape bathed in the warm hues of a sunset or sunrise. The scene is dominated by a large body of water, presumably a bay or ocean, reflecting the golden light. A prominent suspension bridge stretches across the water, connecting distant landmasses. A large ship is visible beneath the bridge, adding scale and a sense of activity. The foreground features glimpses of land with vegetation, transitioning into the expansive water and the blurred outline of distant hills. The sky is dramatic, filled with dark, billowing clouds that contrast with the glowing horizon. The overall impression is one of tranquility and natural beauty, with a focus on the interplay between light, water, and architecture.",
